            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/key-lock.png" alt="Key Lock" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Key Lock</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Lock in your key and stay in tune throughout your session.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/logo-circle-next-chords.png" alt="Next Chords" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Next Chord Predictions</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Next chord predictions keep you ahead of the progression.</p></div></div>
