            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/tunes_manager_list.png" alt="Song List Manager" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Song List Manager</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Organize and manage your personal song collection.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/tunes_manager_lyrics_editor.png" alt="Lyrics Editor" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Lyrics Editor</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Edit lyrics and synchronize them with your chords.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/tunes_manager_record_audio.png" alt="Record Audio" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Record Audio</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Record audio directly into your song manager.</p></div></div>
