          <p class="text-gray-300">Real-time detection keeps you locked in during any jam session</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">🎵 Complete Learning Suite</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Metronome, chord library, and traditional tunes all in one app</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">✍️ Create Your Own</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Write, record, and organize your original songs with full editing tools</p>
